msgid "Mouse and input coordinates"
msgstr "Comhordanáidí luiche agus ionchuir"

msgid "About"
msgstr "Maidir"

msgid ""
"The reason for this small tutorial is to clear up many common mistakes about "
"input coordinates, obtaining mouse position and screen resolution, etc."
msgstr ""
"Is é an chúis atá leis an rang teagaisc beag seo ná go leor botúin "
"choitianta a ghlanadh faoi chomhordanáidí ionchuir, suíomh na luiche agus "
"taifeach scáileáin a fháil, etc."

msgid "Hardware display coordinates"
msgstr "Comhordanáidí taispeána crua-earraí"

msgid ""
"Using hardware coordinates makes sense in the case of writing complex UIs "
"meant to run on PC, such as editors, MMOs, tools, etc. However, it does not "
"make as much sense outside of that scope."
msgstr ""
"Tá ciall le comhordanáidí crua-earraí a úsáid i gcás UIanna casta a scríobh "
"atá i gceist le rith ar ríomhaire, mar shampla eagarthóirí, MMOanna, "
"uirlisí, etc. Mar sin féin, ní dhéanann sé an oiread céille taobh amuigh den "
"raon feidhme sin."

