msgid ""
"Alternatively, it's possible to ask the viewport for the mouse position:"
msgstr ""
"De rogha air sin, is féidir suíomh na luiche a iarraidh ar an bport amhairc:"

msgid ""
"When the mouse mode is set to ``Input.MOUSE_MODE_CAPTURED``, the ``event."
"position`` value from ``InputEventMouseMotion`` is the center of the screen. "
"Use ``event.relative`` instead of ``event.position`` and ``event.velocity`` "
"to process mouse movement and position changes."
msgstr ""
"Nuair a shocraítear mód na luiche go ''Input.MOUSE_MODE_CAPTURED'', is é an "
"luach ''event.position'' ó ''InputEventMouseMotion'' lár an scáileáin. Bain "
"úsáid as ''event.relative'' in ionad ''event.position'' agus ''event."
"velocity'' chun gluaiseacht na luiche agus athruithe suímh a phróiseáil."
